{"id": "art-161", "label": "Art. 161", "title": "Art. 161", "slug": "art-161", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 161 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_683984327\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2005\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_683984327\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Cenzorii pot fi <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>,\ncu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> cenzorului expert contabil, care\npoate fi <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;</span> ce exercit&#259; profesia\nindividual ori în forme asociative.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Nu pot fi cenzori, iar dac&#259; au fost <span class=SpellE>ale&#351;i</span>,\ndecad din mandatul lor:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)rudele\nsau afinii pân&#259; la al patrulea grad inclusiv sau <span class=SpellE>so&#355;ii</span>\nadministratorilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)persoanele\ncare primesc sub orice form&#259;, pentru alte <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ii</span>\ndecât aceea de cenzor, un salariu sau o <span class=SpellE>remunera&#355;ie</span>\nde la administratori sau de la societate sau ai c&#259;ror angajatori sunt în\nraporturi contractuale sau se afl&#259; în <span class=SpellE>concuren&#355;&#259;</span>\ncu aceasta;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1329690816\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2004\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1329690816\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)persoanele c&#259;rora le este interzis&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>func&#355;ia</span> de membru al consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv al consiliului de\nsupraveghere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> al directoratului, în temeiul\nart. 73<sup>1</sup>;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)persoanele\ncare, pe durata exercit&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;iilor</span>\nconferite de aceast&#259; calitate, au <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;ii</span>\nde control în cadrul Ministerului <span class=SpellE>Finan&#355;elor</span>\nPublice sau al altor <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;ii</span> publice, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute expres de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Cenzorii sunt <span class=SpellE>remunera&#355;i</span>\ncu o <span class=SpellE>indemniza&#355;ie</span> fix&#259;, determinat&#259;\nprin actul constitutiv sau de adunarea general&#259; care i-a numit.</span></p>"}